{
 "terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux": "bash",
 "python.experiments.enabled": false,
 "python.venvFolders": ["template-python-code-envs", "dataiku-python-code-envs"],
 "python.defaultInterpreterPath": "/home/dataiku/dataiku-python-code-envs/py37-dss/bin/python",
 "launch": {
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "configurations": [
        {
            "name": "Python 3.7 + dku APIs",
            "type": "python",
            "python": "/opt/dataiku/py37-dss/bin/python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "${file}",
            "console": "integratedTerminal"
        },
        {
            "name": "Python 3.6 + dku APIs",
            "type": "python",
            "python": "/opt/dataiku/pyenv/bin/python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "${file}",
            "console": "integratedTerminal"
        },
        {
            "name": "Python: Current Interpreter",
            "type": "python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "${file}",
            "console": "integratedTerminal",
            "args": [
                "run",
                "--params",
                "FECHADATO:10000000,PIB_TRANSFER_PATH_PREFIX:/tmp/,BITACORA_ENV:des,USER:pepe"
            ]
        }
        ,
        {
            "name": "fw-analyticis-bk",
            "type": "python",
            "python": "/home/dataiku/template-python-code-envs/fw-analyticis-bk/bin/python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "",
            "console": "integratedTerminal"
        },
        {
            "name": "Python: Kedro run",
            "type": "python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "/home/dataiku/workspace/project-lib-versioned/kedro_spark/src/kedro_spark/run.py",
            "console": "integratedTerminal",
            "justMyCode": false,
            "cwd": "/home/dataiku/workspace/project-lib-versioned/kedro_spark",
            "args": [
                "run",
                "--params",
                "FECHADATO:10000000,PIB_TRANSFER_PATH_PREFIX:/tmp/,BITACORA_ENV:des,USER:pepe"
            ],
            "env": {
                "PYTHONPATH": "${workspaceFolder}/src/test/test_project/src:${workspaceFolder}/src:${env:PYTHONPATH}"
            }
        },
        {
            "name": "Kedro recipe run",
            "type": "python",
            "request": "launch",
            "program": "${workspaceFolder}/project-lib-versioned/python/test_project/src/test_project/main.py",
            "console": "integratedTerminal",
            "justMyCode": false,
            "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}/project-lib-versioned/python/test_project",
            "args": [
                "run",
                "--params",
                "FECHADATO:10000000,PIB_TRANSFER_PATH_PREFIX:/tmp/,BITACORA_ENV:des,USER:pepe"
            ],
            "env": {
                "PYTHONPATH": "${workspaceFolder}/src/test/test_project/src:${workspaceFolder}/src:${env:PYTHONPATH}"
            }
        }
        ]

    }
}
